WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )


00:00:18.940 --> 00:00:23.880
♪Only after bloom comes fruit♪

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:29.260
♪Who says glory must fade to the past♪

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.010
♪Only through thunder
do you reach the clouds♪

00:00:38.210 --> 00:00:43.120
♪Who made you the crown of every peak♪

00:00:44.650 --> 00:00:47.930
♪I stand at the center of the stage♪

00:00:47.930 --> 00:00:51.000
♪My shadow is pinned against the wall♪

00:00:51.710 --> 00:00:56.660
♪Facing the light earns every medal♪

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:00.880
♪Little birds,
save your needless pecking♪

00:01:00.880 --> 00:01:04.160
♪The open sky rises high♪

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:09.830
♪When night falls,
the moon begins to shine♪

00:01:10.600 --> 00:01:13.860
♪I stand in the heart of these lands♪

00:01:13.860 --> 00:01:17.220
♪My shadow bears no crown or robe♪

00:01:17.630 --> 00:01:23.300
♪Then I know truth needs no disguise♪

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:26.960
♪The green hills see me as I am♪

00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:30.290
♪Like dew, lightning,
and moon on the river♪

00:01:30.690 --> 00:01:34.730
♪Showing me exactly who I am♪

00:01:34.730 --> 00:01:35.980
=The Lead=

00:01:36.020 --> 00:01:37.940
=Episode 12=

00:01:38.120 --> 00:01:38.960
Move, move!

00:01:39.080 --> 00:01:40.040
The cannon's coming!

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:40.960
Come on!

00:01:42.760 --> 00:01:43.600
Make way, move!

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:44.520
Move aside!

00:01:46.010 --> 00:01:46.880
Clear out!

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:47.720
Quick, quick!

00:01:47.920 --> 00:01:48.760
The cannon's coming!

00:01:57.720 --> 00:02:00.160
Bravo!

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:08.440
Bravo!

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:14.320
Bravo!

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:16.720
Bravo!

00:02:45.440 --> 00:02:46.680
Bravo!

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:48.040
Bravo!

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:49.960
Bravo!

00:02:55.160 --> 00:02:56.400
You're doomed!

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:16.680
Comrades, get the cannon ready!

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:36.240
Aim at the target. Fire the cannon!

00:04:13.100 --> 00:04:15.740
(Best wishes for the premiere
of Hong Hu Chi Wei Dui)

00:04:22.520 --> 00:04:23.360
Great!

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:26.040
Great!

00:04:30.080 --> 00:04:30.920
Bravo!

00:04:31.200 --> 00:04:33.200
Bravo!

00:04:39.760 --> 00:04:41.480
Comrades!

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:46.600
The Committee has decided
to reorganize our unit

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:48.280
into the Workers' and Peasants' Red Army,

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:50.200
so that we can march from one victory…

00:04:51.280 --> 00:04:53.360
to another!

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:55.360
Great!

00:05:07.880 --> 00:05:09.080
Draw the curtains!

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.200
Bravo!

00:05:14.520 --> 00:05:15.720
Bravo!

00:05:16.440 --> 00:05:17.640
Bravo!

00:05:19.400 --> 00:05:20.600
Bravo!

00:05:35.640 --> 00:05:36.600
Why still here?

00:05:37.760 --> 00:05:38.720
Leave!

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.320
Run!

00:05:40.600 --> 00:05:41.800
Run! Run!

00:05:42.040 --> 00:05:42.880
Run!

00:05:45.440 --> 00:05:46.280
Don't rush!

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:47.480
Don't panic!

00:07:12.320 --> 00:07:13.280
Hang in there, Nail!

00:07:13.280 --> 00:07:14.360
Hang in there, Sanyuan!

00:07:14.360 --> 00:07:15.200
Hang in there!

00:07:16.440 --> 00:07:17.280
Sanyuan, hang in there!

00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:19.200
Hang in there!

00:07:20.080 --> 00:07:20.920
Talk!

00:07:21.040 --> 00:07:23.110
You two, go inform the doctor first!

00:07:23.110 --> 00:07:24.200
Go, go!

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:25.760
- Okay! Go!
- Hu Sanyuan!

00:07:25.960 --> 00:07:27.950
- Nail, hang in there!
- Hu Sanyuan, say something!

00:07:28.720 --> 00:07:29.880
- Come on!
- How is he?

00:07:29.880 --> 00:07:31.680
- Hang in there!
- Hu Sanyuan, hang in there!

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:33.920
Hang in there, Hu Sanyuan!

00:07:35.030 --> 00:07:36.240
- Don't sleep!
- Come on!

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:37.400
19!

00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:39.000
- 20!
- 21!

00:07:39.000 --> 00:07:39.840
22!

00:07:39.880 --> 00:07:41.280
- 23!
- 24!

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:42.480
- 25!
- 26!

00:07:42.480 --> 00:07:43.880
- 27!
- 28!

00:07:43.880 --> 00:07:44.720
29!

00:07:45.560 --> 00:07:47.200
Who's not here?

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:49.880
Mr. He, it's Yi Qing'e.

00:07:49.880 --> 00:07:50.720
Where's she?

00:07:50.960 --> 00:07:51.800
No idea.

00:08:01.080 --> 00:08:01.920
Laidi.

00:08:03.320 --> 00:08:04.200
Laidi!

00:08:07.920 --> 00:08:08.840
Laidi!

00:08:08.840 --> 00:08:15.840
(Emergency)

00:08:43.080 --> 00:08:43.920
Where's Hu Sanyuan?

00:08:44.480 --> 00:08:45.320
Where's Hu Sanyuan?

00:08:45.870 --> 00:08:46.770
- The emergency room.
- Where's he?

00:08:46.770 --> 00:08:47.920
- The ER.
- How are they?

00:08:47.920 --> 00:08:48.790
- Me yelling?
- Still under treatment.

00:08:48.790 --> 00:08:51.560
Officer, Hu Sanyuan is the one
responsible for the accident.

00:08:51.560 --> 00:08:52.760
He must be dealt with severely!

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:54.520
Shut your filthy mouth!

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:56.720
Hua Caixiang! I warn you!

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:58.040
Watch your political stance!

00:08:58.040 --> 00:08:58.920
Political stance?

00:08:59.440 --> 00:09:00.840
You're the one with no principles!

00:09:00.840 --> 00:09:01.760
You always stir things up!

00:09:01.760 --> 00:09:03.200
My stance? So what if I hit you!

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:04.880
Have you ever had any principles?

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:06.160
Make way, make way.

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:07.080
They're out!

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:09.040
- What?
- Who is it?

00:09:09.040 --> 00:09:09.880
Who is it?

00:09:10.080 --> 00:09:10.920
Who is it?

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:12.840
- Who is it?
- Who?

00:09:13.710 --> 00:09:14.580
Who?

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:16.320
Is Ding Zhisheng's family here?

00:09:16.640 --> 00:09:17.480
Who?

00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:18.480
Nail…

00:09:18.480 --> 00:09:19.480
Who is Ding Zhisheng's family?

00:09:19.480 --> 00:09:20.320
How is he?

00:09:20.650 --> 00:09:21.530
How is he?

00:09:21.560 --> 00:09:22.440
He's dead.

00:09:23.600 --> 00:09:24.520
Dead?

00:09:24.520 --> 00:09:25.680
Who's his family?

00:09:25.680 --> 00:09:26.520
- What?
- Who?

00:09:26.520 --> 00:09:27.780
- Dead?
- Any family member?

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:28.640
Family member?

00:09:29.520 --> 00:09:31.120
His parents are out of town.

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:32.080
They can't come.

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:33.280
- What to do?
- Yeah...

00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:34.600
Then send him to the morgue first.

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:35.480
Someone come along.

00:09:36.040 --> 00:09:37.600
I'll go! I'll go!

00:09:37.600 --> 00:09:39.120
- Quiet down!
- Me! Me!

00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:40.160
Only one person can come.

00:09:40.840 --> 00:09:41.680
I'll go.

00:10:02.280 --> 00:10:03.320
Doctor, I understand.

00:10:03.400 --> 00:10:04.800
I'll notify the family soon.

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:05.880
Please stay.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:10.320
What did he say?

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:12.480
Hu Sanyuan's condition is extremely serious.

00:10:12.920 --> 00:10:14.280
His intestines were almost blown out.

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:16.600
For the surgery, he needs
a family member's signature.

00:10:17.920 --> 00:10:19.240
Family member?

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:21.040
His sister is far away in Jiuyangou.

00:10:22.680 --> 00:10:23.520
Then…

00:10:25.840 --> 00:10:26.840
can you write your name?

00:10:31.080 --> 00:10:31.920
I'll sign.

00:10:34.360 --> 00:10:36.680
You're all his coworkers, right?

00:10:37.040 --> 00:10:37.920
Yes. Yes, we are.

00:10:37.920 --> 00:10:39.840
- Yes, yes.
- He needs surgery immediately.

00:10:39.840 --> 00:10:40.920
The blood bank has no supply.

00:10:40.920 --> 00:10:42.320
Organize blood donors right away.

00:10:42.400 --> 00:10:43.440
What blood?

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:44.480
Type AB.

00:10:44.480 --> 00:10:45.860
- Type AB?
- AB?

00:10:45.880 --> 00:10:47.000
Who has AB blood?

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:48.640
- Who has AB blood?
- Who's AB?

00:10:49.240 --> 00:10:51.040
Me. I'll donate.

00:10:51.760 --> 00:10:53.360
You're pregnant. You can't donate.

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:55.000
Why not? I'm perfectly healthy.

00:10:55.480 --> 00:10:57.600
You wanna save one life by killing another?

00:10:58.040 --> 00:11:00.280
Then… who here has AB blood?

00:11:00.870 --> 00:11:02.050
- Does anyone have AB blood?
- No idea.

00:11:02.050 --> 00:11:03.480
- Who's AB?
- Will type O work?

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:04.840
I'll donate.

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:07.960
Come for testing.

00:11:10.840 --> 00:11:12.080
I faint at the sight of blood.

00:11:13.080 --> 00:11:13.920
Go with me.

00:11:23.120 --> 00:11:24.520
Please be gentle.

00:11:24.720 --> 00:11:25.920
Don't worry. It won't hurt.

00:12:35.640 --> 00:12:36.480
Dizzy?

00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:39.160
Hu Sanyuan has eggs at home.

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:40.520
I'll boil them all for you.

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:42.440
And yours too.

00:12:52.800 --> 00:12:54.160
Look at him…

00:13:10.810 --> 00:13:12.190
Let's just go.

00:13:24.400 --> 00:13:25.240
Stop it!

00:13:27.320 --> 00:13:28.760
I'm from the Security Section.

00:13:28.760 --> 00:13:29.800
I'm here to help.

00:13:30.280 --> 00:13:31.120
Oh?

00:13:31.520 --> 00:13:33.480
Does the Security Section
outrank the police?

00:13:34.200 --> 00:13:35.080
No, of course not.

00:13:37.560 --> 00:13:38.920
What are you looking at? Out!

00:13:44.720 --> 00:13:46.020
- Let me help.
- Stop it.

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:47.560
Security Section.

00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:55.240
Stop.

00:14:00.200 --> 00:14:02.080
He actually still kept this photo!

00:14:03.640 --> 00:14:06.480
He was taken to the
police station because of it.

00:14:07.400 --> 00:14:08.480
Is it Hua Caixiang?

00:14:08.480 --> 00:14:09.960
Yes, it is!

00:14:10.640 --> 00:14:11.920
Are they a couple?

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:14.720
That… I can't really say.

00:14:19.720 --> 00:14:20.920
Come with me!

00:14:21.640 --> 00:14:22.760
Officer, they're here.

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:33.840
Don't stand there. Come here!

00:14:37.680 --> 00:14:38.520
Come.

00:14:45.040 --> 00:14:46.200
What do you want to know?

00:14:46.760 --> 00:14:49.280
We'll speak with her. Please step outside.

00:14:56.000 --> 00:14:57.040
She's terrified.

00:14:57.720 --> 00:14:58.920
I'm staying here.

00:15:02.120 --> 00:15:03.480
What's your name?

00:15:04.280 --> 00:15:05.120
Yi Qing'e.

00:15:05.840 --> 00:15:07.800
"Yi" like easy, "Qing" like green grass,

00:15:07.800 --> 00:15:08.760
and "E" from Dou E Yuan.

00:15:09.320 --> 00:15:11.160
What's Hu Sanyuan to you?

00:15:11.520 --> 00:15:12.560
Biological uncle.

00:15:13.400 --> 00:15:15.760
Did he say anything special to you lately?

00:15:16.280 --> 00:15:17.160
Nothing.

00:15:17.560 --> 00:15:18.480
I'm asking her.

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:21.280
She's scared

00:15:21.280 --> 00:15:23.520
senseless. She can't talk.

00:15:24.720 --> 00:15:25.560
Your name.

00:15:27.520 --> 00:15:28.360
Hua Caixiang.

00:15:29.120 --> 00:15:30.440
What's your relationship with Hu Sanyuan?

00:15:30.640 --> 00:15:31.640
Comrades.

00:15:32.440 --> 00:15:34.280
Someone reported that
your relationship is unusual.

00:15:36.000 --> 00:15:36.840
Sometimes

00:15:37.680 --> 00:15:39.720
we're like inseparable comrades-in-arms.

00:15:39.720 --> 00:15:42.240
Sometimes we're like bitter enemies.

00:15:42.640 --> 00:15:44.480
Someone saw you arguing yesterday.

00:15:46.280 --> 00:15:47.760
Kind of.

00:15:48.320 --> 00:15:49.160
About what?

00:15:49.400 --> 00:15:50.240
Nothing.

00:15:50.640 --> 00:15:51.560
Cooperate with the investigation.

00:15:53.160 --> 00:15:54.440
People argue because

00:15:54.440 --> 00:15:56.120
they want to argue.

00:15:56.720 --> 00:15:58.560
Has he shown any unusual behavior lately?

00:15:58.560 --> 00:15:59.680
Said anything unusual?

00:16:00.800 --> 00:16:02.840
I can't answer that.

00:16:03.200 --> 00:16:05.720
The Hu Sanyuan I know is just an idiot.

00:16:06.080 --> 00:16:07.760
Whether it's his responsibility or not,

00:16:07.760 --> 00:16:09.200
he always rushes to the front.

00:16:09.720 --> 00:16:10.560
Hu Sanyuan

00:16:11.000 --> 00:16:12.600
is arrogant and defiant toward leadership.

00:16:13.200 --> 00:16:15.080
He ignores Director Huang's warnings.

00:16:15.920 --> 00:16:17.720
And now look, someone's dead!

00:16:19.400 --> 00:16:21.400
He sent Nail off to meet Marx.

00:16:22.480 --> 00:16:24.600
Calm yourself. One thing at a time.

00:16:29.000 --> 00:16:29.840
Comrade.

00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:31.040
This was no accident.

00:16:31.520 --> 00:16:33.360
Hu Sanyuan did it on purpose.

00:16:33.360 --> 00:16:34.280
It was deliberate sabotage.

00:16:34.680 --> 00:16:35.720
What proof do you have?

00:16:36.240 --> 00:16:38.520
Our troupe rehearsed this three times.

00:16:38.520 --> 00:16:39.640
Nothing ever went wrong.

00:16:39.640 --> 00:16:41.120
But on opening night,

00:16:41.120 --> 00:16:43.520
with the County Revolutionary
Committee here,

00:16:43.520 --> 00:16:44.360
it suddenly exploded.

00:16:45.560 --> 00:16:47.680
What motive would he have?

00:16:47.680 --> 00:16:50.040
Hu Sanyuan had improper personal conduct,

00:16:50.400 --> 00:16:52.800
so we gave him a major demerit
and one year of probation.

00:16:52.800 --> 00:16:54.640
Moved from lead drummer to kitchen helper,

00:16:54.960 --> 00:16:56.160
he was bitter about it,

00:16:56.160 --> 00:16:57.160
waiting for a chance to get back at us.

00:17:01.840 --> 00:17:02.720
I think

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:06.640
this is a major political incident.

00:17:08.080 --> 00:17:10.000
A counter-revolutionary incident!

00:17:32.800 --> 00:17:34.000
Are you snoring?

00:17:40.400 --> 00:17:42.120
You really are snoring.

00:17:45.920 --> 00:17:47.520
Idiot, your nerves

00:17:48.320 --> 00:17:50.000
are unbelievable.

00:17:51.680 --> 00:17:53.240
You caused such a disaster,

00:17:53.240 --> 00:17:54.640
and you're still sleeping soundly here.

00:17:54.640 --> 00:17:56.360
I haven't had a decent
night's sleep in days!

00:17:56.360 --> 00:17:57.200
Get up!

00:17:58.760 --> 00:17:59.640
And

00:18:01.200 --> 00:18:02.360
clean up your own mess!

00:18:02.360 --> 00:18:03.800
I can't clean it up for you!

00:18:06.400 --> 00:18:07.240
Hu Sanyuan!

00:18:09.240 --> 00:18:10.080
Hu Sanyuan!

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:14.000
Keep pretending.

00:18:16.600 --> 00:18:18.120
You only know how to bully me.

00:18:26.760 --> 00:18:27.760
He woke up?

00:18:40.000 --> 00:18:41.120
Who did you talk to?

00:18:41.560 --> 00:18:42.640
He was snoring.

00:18:45.920 --> 00:18:48.720
You're exhausted. You're hallucinating.

00:18:51.200 --> 00:18:52.040
Watch him for a while.

00:18:52.520 --> 00:18:53.360
I need to go back.

00:19:19.480 --> 00:19:20.960
What are you peeking around for?

00:19:21.920 --> 00:19:23.000
Afraid people won't notice you

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:24.440
sneaking into my place at night?

00:19:24.440 --> 00:19:25.680
I'm keeping watch.

00:19:25.680 --> 00:19:27.000
The kid is watching outside.

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:28.360
Right. Fine.

00:19:33.120 --> 00:19:33.960
Did

00:19:34.040 --> 00:19:35.120
the police question you?

00:19:35.680 --> 00:19:36.680
Of course. How could

00:19:36.920 --> 00:19:38.200
they leave me out of this?

00:19:39.200 --> 00:19:40.120
They questioned you too?

00:19:42.480 --> 00:19:43.640
Listen to me.

00:19:44.400 --> 00:19:46.440
Huang Zhengjing is trying to turn this

00:19:46.440 --> 00:19:48.120
into a political incident.

00:19:50.120 --> 00:19:51.640
I already sensed that.

00:19:52.560 --> 00:19:54.000
Before the police questioned me,

00:19:54.560 --> 00:19:56.120
the Head of Security had told me

00:19:56.960 --> 00:19:58.320
to say that Hu Sanyuan

00:19:58.320 --> 00:20:01.560
built the cannon on his own initiative.

00:20:02.160 --> 00:20:03.120
What did you say?

00:20:03.520 --> 00:20:04.600
What else could I say?

00:20:05.000 --> 00:20:06.480
I told the truth.

00:20:07.160 --> 00:20:09.040
I told Hu Sanyuan to make the cannon.

00:20:09.720 --> 00:20:11.240
The main responsibility lies with me.

00:20:15.840 --> 00:20:17.440
If this gets labeled

00:20:17.440 --> 00:20:18.360
a political incident,

00:20:18.360 --> 00:20:20.360
the whole nature of it changes.

00:20:22.160 --> 00:20:23.200
Huang Zhengjing is

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:25.400
kicking a man when he's down.

00:20:25.400 --> 00:20:26.720
He wants Hu Sanyuan dead!

00:20:27.320 --> 00:20:29.280
He's protecting himself.

00:20:31.080 --> 00:20:32.360
If they define it

00:20:32.360 --> 00:20:34.480
as deliberate sabotage by Hu Sanyuan,

00:20:34.920 --> 00:20:36.640
then he can escape responsibility.

00:20:36.640 --> 00:20:37.840
Then Hu Sanyuan

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:39.920
would be suffering a terrible injustice!

00:20:40.720 --> 00:20:42.320
Are you allowing him to do that?

00:20:44.440 --> 00:20:45.520
What else to do?

00:20:46.640 --> 00:20:48.080
Write a joint petition.

00:20:48.640 --> 00:20:50.720
Appeal to the higher
authorities and the police.

00:20:51.160 --> 00:20:53.760
That was an ordinary stage accident.

00:20:54.160 --> 00:20:56.480
Hu Sanyuan can never be a saboteur.

00:21:06.080 --> 00:21:06.920
Agreed?

00:21:07.720 --> 00:21:08.560
I agree.

00:21:09.320 --> 00:21:10.160
You write the letter.

00:21:11.920 --> 00:21:14.000
We'll all sign it.

00:21:14.280 --> 00:21:15.480
- I'll sign.
- Okay.

00:21:15.800 --> 00:21:16.640
You?

00:21:17.760 --> 00:21:18.600
I'll sign.

00:21:19.760 --> 00:21:20.600
You?

00:21:22.120 --> 00:21:24.520
He's not even out of danger yet.

00:21:24.520 --> 00:21:26.320
The priority is to keep him alive.

00:21:26.320 --> 00:21:28.160
Otherwise, none of this matters anymore.

00:21:28.160 --> 00:21:30.200
And when he's awake,
he's a counterrevolutionary?

00:21:30.480 --> 00:21:31.720
Then he'd better not wake up.

00:21:33.720 --> 00:21:34.560
He Dachui,

00:21:34.920 --> 00:21:37.320
I know you're Huang Zhengjing's favorite,

00:21:37.320 --> 00:21:39.800
but shouldn't a person
have some bottom line?

00:21:39.800 --> 00:21:40.840
Are you going to

00:21:40.840 --> 00:21:42.440
kick him while he's down too?

00:21:42.440 --> 00:21:43.400
How am I kicking him

00:21:43.400 --> 00:21:44.280
while he's down?

00:21:44.600 --> 00:21:46.360
How is standing by and doing nothing

00:21:46.360 --> 00:21:47.360
any different from that?

00:21:47.360 --> 00:21:48.800
I never said I wouldn't sign.

00:21:48.800 --> 00:21:51.120
I mean, Mi Lan should sign too.

00:21:51.440 --> 00:21:53.440
She's the lead actress. If she signs,

00:21:53.440 --> 00:21:55.120
it'll be more convincing.

00:21:55.120 --> 00:21:56.360
No way.

00:21:56.680 --> 00:21:58.680
She's suffering enough already.

00:21:59.520 --> 00:22:02.680
She finally got the chance to be the lead,

00:22:02.920 --> 00:22:03.760
and after just one show,

00:22:04.120 --> 00:22:05.440
before she could even take her

00:22:06.440 --> 00:22:08.240
curtain call, the blast destroyed it all.

00:22:08.860 --> 00:22:09.800
Hu Sanyuan's

00:22:09.800 --> 00:22:11.480
got her blood running through him.

00:22:11.480 --> 00:22:12.800
Shut your mouth.

00:22:12.960 --> 00:22:14.280
I mean, she

00:22:14.280 --> 00:22:15.480
donated blood for him.

00:22:15.480 --> 00:22:17.080
She wanted to save him.

00:22:17.080 --> 00:22:19.120
Of course, she'll sign. Right?

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:31.240
Write it.

00:22:41.280 --> 00:22:43.240
Everyone says you're smart,

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:47.320
but honestly, you're a fool.

00:22:49.560 --> 00:22:51.680
You had a broad road ahead of you,

00:22:52.800 --> 00:22:54.600
yet you only walked the narrow bridge.

00:22:58.640 --> 00:23:00.120
Being a good person

00:23:01.320 --> 00:23:03.280
doesn't mean you'll have a good fate.

00:23:04.600 --> 00:23:06.000
Beating drums well

00:23:07.520 --> 00:23:10.320
doesn't mean you can fire a cannon well.

00:23:12.720 --> 00:23:14.280
After all these years,

00:23:16.560 --> 00:23:19.480
I finally became the lead once,

00:23:21.560 --> 00:23:25.120
finally stood center stage

00:23:25.640 --> 00:23:27.280
carrying the show…

00:23:33.720 --> 00:23:35.480
I really thought this time

00:23:37.240 --> 00:23:40.840
you'd fire one shot and
give me an exclamation mark.

00:23:44.120 --> 00:23:47.440
But instead, you turned it into a period.

00:24:03.800 --> 00:24:04.640
Brother…

00:24:06.480 --> 00:24:07.600
I wasn't blaming you.

00:24:15.080 --> 00:24:15.920
What?

00:24:19.320 --> 00:24:20.800
I heard him snoring.

00:24:22.760 --> 00:24:24.000
Even unconscious,

00:24:24.600 --> 00:24:26.080
this idiot still won't behave.

00:24:36.920 --> 00:24:37.760
How would you

00:24:39.640 --> 00:24:40.800
describe Hu Sanyuan?

00:24:41.720 --> 00:24:42.560
What do you mean?

00:24:43.040 --> 00:24:44.520
If he never wakes up,

00:24:45.040 --> 00:24:46.600
I'm engraving this on his tombstone:

00:24:47.280 --> 00:24:48.280
"No disturbing.

00:24:48.760 --> 00:24:50.440
This ghost won't stay quiet."

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:54.240
Then I'll engrave:

00:24:54.840 --> 00:24:55.680
"No fear.

00:24:56.720 --> 00:24:58.000
He's just a foolish ghost."

00:24:59.560 --> 00:25:00.400
How's he foolish?

00:25:00.800 --> 00:25:02.840
If not, would he have
blown himself up like this?

00:25:08.520 --> 00:25:10.000
A foolish ghost,

00:25:10.560 --> 00:25:12.080
a restless ghost,

00:25:13.160 --> 00:25:14.920
even a romantic ghost... Fine.

00:25:16.480 --> 00:25:18.360
But he must not be a wronged ghost.

00:25:25.480 --> 00:25:26.320
Say something.

00:25:27.120 --> 00:25:28.560
Whatever you say.

00:25:29.440 --> 00:25:30.720
I'm not qualified to judge him.

00:25:31.160 --> 00:25:32.240
You know very well

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:33.880
how much he's helped you all these years,

00:25:34.240 --> 00:25:35.080
openly and secretly.

00:25:39.320 --> 00:25:40.160
Sister,

00:25:41.000 --> 00:25:42.280
if you need me to do something,

00:25:42.280 --> 00:25:43.600
just say it.

00:25:48.480 --> 00:25:49.320
Listen.

00:25:50.520 --> 00:25:53.160
Huang claims this was deliberate sabotage.

00:25:53.680 --> 00:25:54.840
He wants to turn it into

00:25:55.200 --> 00:25:56.520
a counterrevolutionary incident.

00:25:57.440 --> 00:25:59.000
We've all written and signed

00:25:59.280 --> 00:26:00.240
a joint petition

00:26:00.720 --> 00:26:02.040
to clear his name.

00:26:02.320 --> 00:26:03.280
You should sign too.

00:26:03.760 --> 00:26:04.800
There's strength in numbers.

00:26:13.200 --> 00:26:14.080
Whatever.

00:26:14.960 --> 00:26:16.280
After all, you gave him blood.

00:26:16.960 --> 00:26:17.920
Pretend it was wasted.

00:26:27.600 --> 00:26:28.440
What?

00:26:40.600 --> 00:26:42.640
You wrote a petition to defend him too?

00:26:42.960 --> 00:26:44.240
If you think it's okay,

00:26:44.800 --> 00:26:46.360
sign it.

00:26:48.000 --> 00:26:49.800
I already signed first, so you'll

00:26:50.440 --> 00:26:51.800
have to sign after me.

00:27:00.240 --> 00:27:01.080
Ms. Hua.

00:27:02.600 --> 00:27:03.600
Ms. Mi Lan.

00:27:03.600 --> 00:27:04.440
Sis.

00:27:05.720 --> 00:27:07.080
Has he woken up yet?

00:27:08.240 --> 00:27:10.120
His body's awake. His soul isn't.

00:27:11.280 --> 00:27:12.640
After a cannon that thick exploded,

00:27:13.120 --> 00:27:14.800
nobody's soul could take it.

00:27:15.680 --> 00:27:16.520
What is it?

00:27:27.080 --> 00:27:27.920
What?

00:27:28.400 --> 00:27:29.960
Did you write a joint petition

00:27:30.360 --> 00:27:31.320
for him?

00:27:31.960 --> 00:27:32.840
How did you know?

00:27:33.440 --> 00:27:35.600
Qiu and Master Song signed it too.

00:27:37.080 --> 00:27:38.200
What do you mean?

00:27:38.640 --> 00:27:40.000
Can temporary workers sign too?

00:27:40.680 --> 00:27:42.160
Add my name.

00:27:44.240 --> 00:27:45.320
No matter what,

00:27:46.800 --> 00:27:48.480
he once helped me knead dough.

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:55.560
Sure.

00:28:33.520 --> 00:28:34.760
How's your uncle?

00:28:40.960 --> 00:28:41.960
They said

00:28:42.440 --> 00:28:44.200
he was revived.

00:28:47.160 --> 00:28:48.120
Chu Jiahe said…

00:28:48.960 --> 00:28:50.200
her dad said

00:28:51.800 --> 00:28:55.240
your uncle might be a counterrevolutionary.

00:28:56.800 --> 00:28:58.680
Even if they save him,

00:28:59.680 --> 00:29:01.040
he'll still "eat peanuts".

00:29:02.440 --> 00:29:03.960
What does "eat peanuts" mean?

00:29:05.360 --> 00:29:06.480
They say

00:29:07.520 --> 00:29:09.760
"eating peanuts" means taking bullets.

00:29:11.840 --> 00:29:12.920
Getting executed.

00:29:56.560 --> 00:29:58.520
Someone got blown to death.

00:29:59.120 --> 00:30:01.080
Is her uncle actually the murderer?

00:30:01.880 --> 00:30:04.440
- Yeah..
- If you kill someone, you go to jail.

00:30:05.320 --> 00:30:06.160
Right.

00:30:07.040 --> 00:30:07.880
I don't know.

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:10.560
He used that much gunpowder.

00:30:10.560 --> 00:30:11.720
On purpose?

00:30:11.720 --> 00:30:12.640
Otherwise, why

00:30:13.160 --> 00:30:15.640
would he use so much gunpowder?

00:30:16.200 --> 00:30:18.080
- Really?
- Died?

00:30:18.120 --> 00:30:18.960
Will he

00:30:19.720 --> 00:30:21.440
have to compensate the family?

00:30:21.440 --> 00:30:22.280
Maybe.

00:30:27.440 --> 00:30:28.280
Who?

00:30:28.400 --> 00:30:30.160
Me. Yi Qing'e.

00:30:30.780 --> 00:30:31.930
- Why's she here?
- What does she want?

00:30:32.480 --> 00:30:33.320
Dumb.

00:30:35.840 --> 00:30:36.680
What?

00:30:40.920 --> 00:30:41.960
Chu Jiahe,

00:30:43.240 --> 00:30:44.520
can you come out for a second?

00:30:44.960 --> 00:30:45.800
What is it?

00:30:45.960 --> 00:30:47.120
It's important.

00:30:48.040 --> 00:30:49.320
Please come out.

00:30:51.040 --> 00:30:52.320
Why does she want Jiahe?

00:30:52.320 --> 00:30:53.160
Then just go.

00:30:53.520 --> 00:30:54.360
What is it?

00:31:01.320 --> 00:31:02.160
What?

00:31:06.120 --> 00:31:06.960
Stop staring.

00:31:07.320 --> 00:31:08.840
Go inside. Close the door.

00:31:14.040 --> 00:31:14.880
Talk.

00:31:19.360 --> 00:31:20.200
What's this?

00:31:21.080 --> 00:31:23.560
A new dress. I only wore it once.

00:31:24.000 --> 00:31:24.840
It's for you.

00:31:25.800 --> 00:31:26.680
Why?

00:31:29.240 --> 00:31:30.600
Please… ask your dad

00:31:31.920 --> 00:31:33.440
to save my uncle.

00:31:38.320 --> 00:31:39.520
I beg you.

00:31:43.080 --> 00:31:44.560
Nobody can save him now.

00:31:49.400 --> 00:31:50.440
Jiahe's back.

00:31:50.960 --> 00:31:51.960
Jiahe. Jiahe.

00:31:52.200 --> 00:31:53.240
What happened?

00:31:53.240 --> 00:31:55.200
What did she say?

00:31:55.760 --> 00:31:56.600
What is it?

00:31:57.360 --> 00:31:58.560
That idiot wanted my dad

00:31:59.040 --> 00:32:00.040
to save her uncle.

00:32:00.040 --> 00:32:02.080
What?

00:32:02.360 --> 00:32:03.200
Shameless.

00:32:03.200 --> 00:32:05.040
Her uncle was arrested many times.

00:32:05.280 --> 00:32:06.280
Isn't he dead?

00:32:06.280 --> 00:32:07.720
Two or three times already.

00:32:08.080 --> 00:32:09.000
So he's not dead.

00:32:09.880 --> 00:32:12.360
He got arrested for an illicit affair.

00:32:12.480 --> 00:32:14.000
- Remember?
- Yeah.

00:32:14.000 --> 00:32:15.160
Now, again?

00:32:57.960 --> 00:32:58.800
Come.

00:33:29.480 --> 00:33:30.360
Quietly!

00:33:31.840 --> 00:33:32.680
I know, I know.

00:33:43.440 --> 00:33:44.440
Here, here!

00:34:22.280 --> 00:34:23.760
Don't cause more trouble.

00:34:23.760 --> 00:34:25.320
Her uncle got somebody killed!

00:34:25.320 --> 00:34:26.760
Did he hurt you?

00:34:41.640 --> 00:34:42.720
Want some Mo?

00:34:42.720 --> 00:34:44.080
She doesn't want it.

00:34:44.080 --> 00:34:45.160
Let's go.

00:34:46.320 --> 00:34:47.160
Come on.

00:34:47.360 --> 00:34:48.680
Let's make a bet.

00:34:49.480 --> 00:34:51.160
Why suddenly a bet?

00:34:52.320 --> 00:34:53.160
Bet on what?

00:34:53.440 --> 00:34:55.200
I bet her uncle, Hu Sanyuan,

00:34:55.200 --> 00:34:57.520
will come through this safely.

00:34:58.200 --> 00:35:00.320
But the police won't agree to that.

00:35:01.680 --> 00:35:02.520
Fine, I'm in.

00:35:02.720 --> 00:35:03.880
How?

00:35:03.880 --> 00:35:05.600
Rock-paper-scissors. Best two out of three.

00:35:06.640 --> 00:35:07.960
Okay. Best two out of three.

00:35:08.240 --> 00:35:09.320
Rock-paper-scissors.

00:35:09.720 --> 00:35:10.680
Rock-paper-scissors.

00:35:11.440 --> 00:35:12.280
Rock-paper...

00:35:12.440 --> 00:35:13.360
Rock-paper-scissors.

00:35:14.280 --> 00:35:15.720
Wow, you won

00:35:15.720 --> 00:35:17.560
all three rounds!

00:35:18.880 --> 00:35:21.560
See, Laidi? I won all three.

00:35:21.840 --> 00:35:24.320
I told you your uncle's gonna be fine.

00:35:24.760 --> 00:35:26.480
Stop worrying, okay?

00:35:27.320 --> 00:35:28.160
Eat.

00:35:31.960 --> 00:35:33.080
Dummy, why are you crying?

00:35:33.560 --> 00:35:34.560
I'm not dumb!

00:35:38.360 --> 00:35:40.520
Okay, okay, you're not dumb. Why yelling?

00:35:41.160 --> 00:35:42.000
Eat.

00:35:48.780 --> 00:35:51.540
(Three months later...
Ningzhou Department Store)

00:35:52.000 --> 00:35:53.000
Students,

00:35:53.000 --> 00:35:55.320
today we're learning from
Lei Feng by doing good deeds!

00:35:55.320 --> 00:35:57.560
We should not only learn from
his willingness to help others,

00:35:57.560 --> 00:36:00.640
but also from his serious
attitude toward work!

00:36:00.640 --> 00:36:03.200
Sweep properly! Make it cleaner!

00:36:06.480 --> 00:36:07.320
Yi Qing'e!

00:36:07.520 --> 00:36:08.360
Yi Qing'e!

00:36:08.680 --> 00:36:09.560
Stop working and come with me.

00:36:09.760 --> 00:36:10.600
What for?

00:36:10.640 --> 00:36:11.560
Hurry. Don't ask.

00:36:11.560 --> 00:36:13.360
Quick, quick. Let's go. Hurry.

00:36:16.280 --> 00:36:17.120
Right here.

00:36:23.500 --> 00:36:26.580
(Pharmacy)

00:36:33.960 --> 00:36:34.800
Comrade,

00:36:35.160 --> 00:36:36.920
this is Hu Sanyuan's niece.

00:36:37.320 --> 00:36:38.520
- Let her see him.
- Go in.

00:36:38.600 --> 00:36:40.240
Go see your uncle. Hurry.

00:37:00.320 --> 00:37:01.600
I am sorry.

00:37:05.440 --> 00:37:06.720
I did something foolish.

00:37:08.520 --> 00:37:09.720
I caused Nail's death,

00:37:11.280 --> 00:37:12.560
and I dragged all of you into this.

00:37:15.240 --> 00:37:16.880
I'll never forgive myself.

00:37:19.160 --> 00:37:20.680
I'm going to be punished.

00:37:23.360 --> 00:37:24.200
I deserve it.

00:37:25.080 --> 00:37:26.280
I brought this upon myself.

00:37:30.160 --> 00:37:32.320
I only want to ask you one thing.

00:37:35.680 --> 00:37:37.880
You must keep learning the opera,

00:37:39.840 --> 00:37:43.040
no matter how hard or exhausting it gets.

00:37:47.120 --> 00:37:48.720
If you give up halfway,

00:37:49.240 --> 00:37:53.200
then it'll mean I truly
accomplished nothing.

00:37:55.000 --> 00:37:58.600
This whole half of my life was wasted.

00:38:04.000 --> 00:38:04.840
Promise me.

00:38:08.400 --> 00:38:10.280
I need to hear you promise me.

00:38:12.560 --> 00:38:15.520
I… I promise you.

00:39:04.480 --> 00:39:05.320
Sanyuan!

00:40:37.810 --> 00:40:41.400
♪Last year on this very day,
within this gate♪

00:40:45.960 --> 00:40:47.000
Laidi!

00:40:50.790 --> 00:40:55.960
♪That lovely face, where has it gone♪

00:40:56.950 --> 00:41:01.670
♪Only the peach blossoms remain smiling♪

00:41:18.520 --> 00:41:19.880
Hu Sanyuan left.

00:41:20.400 --> 00:41:21.840
He was taken away in handcuffs.

00:41:22.760 --> 00:41:25.320
He had brought Yi Qing'e
out of the mountains,

00:41:25.320 --> 00:41:28.440
yet sent himself into prison.

00:41:29.600 --> 00:41:31.680
Yi Qing'e could not bear to part with him.

00:41:32.200 --> 00:41:33.040
That day,

00:41:33.280 --> 00:41:38.040
she understood how painful it was.

00:41:38.040 --> 00:41:39.360
Uncle!

00:41:40.680 --> 00:41:41.880
Uncle!

00:41:58.320 --> 00:42:01.600
To build a powerful
socialist modernized nation,

00:42:01.600 --> 00:42:03.880
we must make tremendous efforts

00:42:03.880 --> 00:42:06.400
to accelerate the development
of the national economy

00:42:06.400 --> 00:42:08.520
and fight this crucial ten-year battle,

00:42:08.760 --> 00:42:10.120
so that within this century

00:42:10.120 --> 00:42:14.560
our country may become a
strong modern socialist nation.

00:42:17.510 --> 00:42:22.210
♪Husband and wife parted by life and death♪

00:42:22.740 --> 00:42:28.180
♪The deepest sorrow in this world♪

00:42:30.810 --> 00:42:33.270
♪For a month now♪

00:42:33.270 --> 00:42:39.490
♪Grief has been buried within my heart♪

00:42:39.910 --> 00:42:44.410
♪Tonight the moon is dim♪

00:42:44.410 --> 00:42:49.280
♪The wilderness is silent♪

00:42:49.960 --> 00:42:52.350
♪Cold and desolate♪

00:42:52.920 --> 00:42:57.230
♪Beyond the lonely outskirts♪

00:43:00.320 --> 00:43:02.840
Aunt Hua… I want to go home.

00:43:05.020 --> 00:43:06.940
=The Lead=
(Preview)

00:43:09.110 --> 00:43:10.760
Hu Sanyuan's already in prison,

00:43:10.760 --> 00:43:12.760
and now you won't even spare his kid?

00:43:14.480 --> 00:43:16.710
Kid, where's your exit pass?

00:43:17.000 --> 00:43:19.440
From now on, Master Song is your teacher.

00:43:19.440 --> 00:43:20.840
You sing opera to earn a meal.

00:43:20.840 --> 00:43:22.670
Tending the stove brings you
closer to the cooking pot.

00:43:22.670 --> 00:43:24.320
Do you really love singing opera that much?

00:43:24.320 --> 00:43:25.710
The reason for the fight isn't important.

00:43:25.710 --> 00:43:27.960
What matters is that it is with you.

00:43:27.960 --> 00:43:29.320
I'm leaving.

00:43:29.320 --> 00:43:30.760
Going somewhere else...

00:43:30.760 --> 00:43:32.320
to sing a different story.

00:43:37.000 --> 00:43:41.620
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:43:43.090 --> 00:43:47.930
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:43:49.370 --> 00:43:53.560
♪We met and brushed past♪

00:43:55.120 --> 00:44:02.420
♪Your shadow drifted out of sight♪

00:44:16.790 --> 00:44:20.540
♪The stove fire blazed in my dream♪

00:44:22.140 --> 00:44:27.710
♪Lit up the tracks of pearly tears♪

00:44:28.830 --> 00:44:32.890
♪In my dream, water sleeves flew♪

00:44:34.020 --> 00:44:39.610
♪Hiding a lifetime of love♪

00:44:40.770 --> 00:44:44.970
♪The Qinling Mountains
crossed the stage♪

00:44:46.010 --> 00:44:51.640
♪Spring water brewed strong wine♪

00:44:52.810 --> 00:44:57.500
♪Sheep moved through the valley♪

00:44:58.180 --> 00:45:03.350
♪It felt like a promise
from another life♪

00:45:04.020 --> 00:45:09.050
♪When I woke up and turned back♪

00:45:10.080 --> 00:45:15.510
♪I wasn't sure where to go♪

00:45:15.890 --> 00:45:21.170
♪If I chose again, I'd still roam♪

00:45:22.120 --> 00:45:27.930
♪All over this sunlit plateau♪

00:45:27.930 --> 00:45:33.350
♪The dream ends; the curtain falls♪

00:45:33.900 --> 00:45:39.410
♪Moonlight washes off this stage makeup♪

00:45:39.960 --> 00:45:44.920
♪The one in the mirror wears gray hair♪

00:45:45.940 --> 00:45:51.220
♪Already sang all my joy and sorrow♪

